        <name>adsp_hda_log_hook_t</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>HDA logger requires a hook for IPC messages. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>When the log is flushed and written with DMA an IPC message should be sent to inform the host. This hook function pointer allows for that </para>
